testsuite.name: InstructorRepository Sorting Tests

testcase.name: sortByExpertiseAndName should sort by expertise desc then name
sorting empty repository should return empty list
sortByExpertiseAndName should handle multiple instructors with same expertise
sortByExpertise with same expertise should maintain stable order
sorting should not modify the original repository
sortByLastNameLength should sort by lastName length
sortByLastName should sort by lastName then firstName
sorting single instructor should return list with that instructor
sortByFirstName should sort by firstName then lastName
sortByExpertise should sort by expertise descending
